      <title>中国批准阿斯利康和赛诺菲注射预防 RSV 感染</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-02/china-approves-astrazeneca-sanofi-shot-to-prevent-rsv-infection</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国批准了阿斯利康公司和赛诺菲共同开发的一种疫苗，用于预防大量婴儿感染呼吸道合胞病毒，这是该国首次阻止这种高度传染性和可能致命的感染。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-02/china-approves-astrazeneca-sanofi-shot-to-prevent-rsv-infection</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 09:14:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>SBB暂停支付4900万美元债券以缓解资金紧缩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-02/landlord-sbb-seen-saving-50-million-on-pause-of-hybrid-payments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[北极证券 (Arctic Securities) 分析师称，陷入困境的瑞典房东 SBB 决定暂停其混合债券的利息支付，将为该公司每年节省约 4.96 亿瑞典克朗（合 4,920 万美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-02/landlord-sbb-seen-saving-50-million-on-pause-of-hybrid-payments</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 09:01:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国年初发放大量原油进口配额</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-02/china-issues-massive-crude-oil-import-quotas-at-start-of-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国提前加载了2024年的石油进口配额，分配给私营炼油厂和贸易商的配额几乎与去年全年的所有配额相当。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-02/china-issues-massive-crude-oil-import-quotas-at-start-of-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 08:46:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
